listing.description:
Aphrodite's Vision™ is the one luxurious body oil you'll ever need. Our oil is specially formulated with ingredients such as Meadowfoam Seed, Macadamia Nut, and Argan oils. Our oil is rich, light weight and easily absorbs without leaving behind an oily residue like most other body oils will. Hints of sweet florals, citrus and vanilla make this scent otherworldly! 

This beautiful blend contains and is charged with rose quartz crystals. Rose quartz is a crystal of love, romance, friendship and healing communication. Tap into the energy/frequency of love with goddess Aphrodite. Love is the highest vibrational state to be in.   

This beautiful oil was made in her honor and honor of my ancestors of Thrace (current Bulgaria). The mention of Aphrodite pre dates Greek times and she was originally worshipped by the civilization that inhabited the Balkans. The Thrace civilization being one of them. She was a Thracian deity (later adapted by the Greeks). The protobúlgaros, also know as ancient Bulgarians, (Thracians) had beliefs structured on paganism and worshipped different goddesses/deities. Aphrodite was one of them. A portion of her name, Αβеρε- spelled Αβеρεδιτα (Aberedita in English) corresponds to the Phrygian verb (which is a Indo-European language related to the Thracians) αββеρε which means to bring, or to collect. The other part of the name διτα, which is the equivalent to the Bulgarian word “ditsa” (English spelling) and means children. The correct name of the goddess of love is Aberedita, and its meaning is “the one that brings children”, or “the one with children”. She was known as the goddess of fertility, in addition to being the goddess of love and beauty. In those times, fertility was more sought after and more valued than beauty.

Use oil when desired or when you want to treat yourself to a luxurious afterbath ritual. Enhance your self-care routine and bring out your inner goddess.

How to use: To open cap, pull it off (not twist). Press the pump to dispense oil and apply on desired area. 

Phthalate free, paraben-free, vegan and cruelty free. Luxury oil comes in a beautiful 3.5 oz elegant glass bottle. 

☾ Click here for the Aphrodite’s Vision Luxury Perfume Oil and Ritual Oil.
~ Perfume Oil: https://www.etsy.com/listing/1027181842/aphrodites-vision-luxury-ritual-spell?ref=shop_home_active_2
~ Ritual Oil: https://www.etsy.com/listing/1027184030/aphrodites-vision-luxury-ritual-spell?ref=shop_home_active_3

All items are sold as curios. 

All content is ©Eternally Arcane®

🔮🌜 This is a handmade shop, therefore all sales are final. Before checkout, please make sure the items in your cart are the ones that you want. Thank you!

🔮✨Join our spiritual community!🔮✨ 
🌙Connect with us @eternallyarcane on Instagram, Facebook, and TikTok for updates on new product releases, sale events, inspiration, and more!✨

policies.additional:
- Welcome to my shop! I make sure every magickal item is made with the highest vibrations and quality ingredients. If you have any questions or concerns regarding your order, please feel free to contact me first. 

Cancellation Requests:

Due to the nature of our products, we do not grant cancellations. They are handmade, so a lot of time goes into making them. Please be mindful of this before purchasing. Make sure that your order is accurate before you complete your purchase. Thank you for your understanding.

If you've already placed your order and decide to add more items, please place a separate order since we cannot manually add items or edit your current order. 

Returns and Refunds: 

Due to the nature of our items, we do not accept returns, unless it is approved by us. Unauthorized/forced returns will not be refunded. Our products are artisan, one of kind, and limited edition. A lot of work and energy goes into each product. Spiritual products become affected by different energies so we cannot resale them. This is due to spiritual reasons as well as hygienic reasons. All of our products are brand new and freshly made for our customers. 

Exchanges, Replacements/Damaged Items, and Weather Conditions:

Exchanges: We don't accept exchanges as all our items are delivered in brand new condition to ensure the best experience for our customers.

Replacements/Damaged Items: We do everything we can to ensure the quality and condition of our products. With that said, we understand that sometimes things don’t work out, and that the postal system can be rough with deliveries at times. We do make sure to protectively wrap every product so that it can arrive to you safely and in one piece. Despite our efforts, sometimes things don't go as planned. We recommend you to inspect your order upon delivery and contact us immediately if the item is defective or damaged, so that we can evaluate the issue and make it right. Send us a photo of the damaged item within 24 hours. Please be aware that we cannot accept any claims for items beyond the time frame of 24 hours after you receive the merchandise. No exceptions. 

Weather Conditions: We unfortunately cannot predict the severity of the weather conditions and as to whether or not they will impact the product or delivery. Due to factors beyond our control, such as the weather, we are unable to provide replacements for products that may become damaged (such as breakage due to freezing of an oil and other liquid products, or melting of candles etc.) because of severe weather conditions or natural disasters. It’s best to avoid ordering products, whether candles or oils, when temperatures in your area are at or below freezing, or during periods of extreme heat. Please be mindful of this before ordering as we cannot refund or replace items damaged due to natural weather conditions. You can always place your order once the weather conditions improve in your area.

Shipping Address:

Customers are solely responsible for providing their accurate shipping address during checkout. In the event that items are shipped to an incorrect address due to customer negligence, refunds will not be issued. If an item is returned to us due to wrong address entered, we will process a refund for your order amount, but please note that a 25% restocking fee of the total order amount will be applied to cover the labor and packaging costs associated with your order. Additionally, the shipping fee, which has already been rendered, will not be refunded. Please note that we cannot verify the accuracy of the customer's address entered during checkout, and therefore, we do not assume any responsibility in this regard. Please make sure that your shipping address is correct before placing your order with us. Thank you for your understanding.

Should you have a change of heart and no longer wish to keep your order, please be aware that we will not issue refunds for refused packages or unauthorized returns. Buyer covers the shipping costs if they would like a reshipment after an incorrect address was entered. You’re welcome to contact us so we can arrange that for you. We do not accept returns as these are artisan products.

Processing and Shipping: 

Orders are processed in the order they are received. Our current processing time is 3-7 business days (Monday-Friday). This is the amount of time it takes for us to make, package, and label your order, then send it out to the post office. We do not process orders on holidays or weekends. Around the Holiday season, processing times may be longer. Please make sure to check back here, or our shop announcement for our updated processing times, as they can sometimes change. When your order ships, you will receive a notification in your email, and on the Etsy app that your order is on its way, along with a tracking number. You may also find the tracking number in your account under your "purchases". Please allow USPS to update their tracking in the system 24-48 hours after the label has been created. Sometimes USPS doesn't scan package right away. 

If you opt for Priority Mail Shipping, or Priority Mail Express, this does not change the processing time on our end, it only changes the transit time with USPS. 

For orders marked as gifts, please enter the address of your recipient and we will send the package directly to them if you'd like. If you're wanting to purchase products for multiple friends, or family, please place your orders separately and enter each address for each person accordingly. 

Please make sure that all items you want to purchase are in your cart at checkout, since we cannot edit orders, (add or remove items) once the order is placed.

All orders are shipped via USPS with tracking.

We operate and ship from California, USA. All products are hand made in the USA.

Lost, stolen, and misdelivered packages or packages that were marked as delivered but are not there:

Eternally Arcane® is not liable for stolen, misdelivered, or packages that were marked as delivered but are not there. We are only liable for the package from the time it leaves our business and to the post office. On the rare instance, if any of the above issues occur, please contact USPS. You may have to file a theft report if your package was stolen from your residence and can't be found, or fill out a missing mail form with USPS if the package is lost. Please contact your local post office that services your area within 30 days of the purchase, or call the USPS hotline. The USPS hotline number is 1-800-275-8777. You may also visit their official USPS website to fill out their missing mail form. They will provide you with the necessary steps to retrieve your package.

International Buyers Please Note. Very Important!

Import duties and taxes are not included in the price or the shipping charges. The buyer is liable for these charges. If there is a concern about import duties or taxes, please check with your country's customs office prior to purchasing. 

Import restrictions in your country: The buyer should be aware what type of products are allowed to pass through to their country and what kind of products are restricted. It's also the buyers duty to be aware of any custom fees, taxes, shipping fees or any additional expenses that may occur. Please double check with your country's regulations, and customs office before placing your order. If a package gets returned to us because the item is restricted and not allowed in your country, or you did not pay fee requirements, or the package gets lost, stolen, or misdelivered, we cannot issue a refund. Shipping international is a higher risk. Please make note of this prior to purchasing! International packages usually take between 3-5 weeks to arrive. We are not liable for customs delays, or delays from a third party shipping forwarding service.

Shipping Forwarding Services:

If you use a shipping forwarding service, we are not liable for lost or stolen items. These are 3rd party shipping providers and are not associated with our business. There are no refunds for lost, stolen, or missing items. Any lost or stolen items need to be addressed with your 3rd party shipping provider.

Gifts:

If your order is a gift, please mark it as such and the invoice will be left out of the order. You can also include a gift message with your order. Please note that for gifts, the 3-7 business day processing time is still needed to fulfill all orders. As another option, you can use Etsy's rough estimated time of arrival for reference which is shown on all of our product listings. But please note that Etsy's estimate is not always accurate. Consider our shop's processing time and USPS transit time when ordering gifts so that you can have an estimate of when your order will arrive. Keep in mind that we cannot control any USPS shipping delays if they occur. Thank you ❤️

Coupon Codes:

For discounts, coupon codes must be applied during checkout. We are unable to apply coupon codes after they have expired or after checkout. The system does not accept them. Please note that these coupon codes are limited to one per customer. Coupon codes cannot be combined with other codes. 

Sale Events: 

Discounts cannot be applied to orders placed prior to the sale event. Orders cannot be canceled. 

Free Shipping:

All orders are shipped via USPS. We offer free complimentary shipping on all US orders that value $35.00 or more (we pay the shipping). The free shipping option will be shown once your order meets the $35.00 minimum. 

Wholesale and Custom Orders:

We do not accept wholesale or custom orders at this time. 

Patch Testing New Skincare Products:

Allergy Information - Patch testing a new skin care product:

The AAD (American Academy of Dermatology) recommends the following steps: Apply the product to a small patch of skin where a person is unlikely to accidentally wash or rub it away. Good areas may include the inside of the arm or bend of the elbow. Apply the product to a quarter-sized patch of skin. A person should apply the product as thickly as they would when using it regularly. Leave the product on the patch of skin for as long as it would normally be on the skin. Repeat the patch test twice a day for between 7–10 days. Wash off and discontinue use if irritation occurs. We are not medical professionals so using any skincare products, or products with herbs, essential oils, or fragrance oils, is at the sole discretion of the customer.

A patch test is highly recommended for all skincare products. Consult with your doctor if in doubt on using products with herbs, essential oils or fragrance oils. There is a possibility that some people may have allergic reactions to various things. By purchasing from us, you agree that we will not be held liable for allergic reactions and that there will be no refunds.

Body products such as perfume oils, ritual oils, soaps etc. are for EXTERNAL USE ONLY. Avoid using on eyes and face and avoid open flames. By purchasing from Eternally Arcane®, you have read, fully understand and agree to all of the information in our product descriptions, our Privacy Policy and the FAQ and any other information presented in regards to our products. 

Disclaimer:

Our products are based on preserving traditions and are intended as aids in ritual and spiritual work. All information stated throughout the shop is for informational purposes only, and should never be substituted for medical advice. As with all spiritual products on the market, Eternally Arcane® does not guarantee results and they may vary for each individual. In no event shall our business Eternally Arcane®, be liable for any direct, indirect, punitive, incidental, special consequential damages, to property or life, whatsoever arising out of or connected with the use or misuse of our products. By purchasing our products and using our services, you have read, and agree to release us from any and all liability. You accept our Terms & Conditions and our Policy, and understand that you take sole responsibility for the use of any of our products and release Eternally Arcane® from any and all liability. This is a mandatory disclaimer. Thank you for understanding.

Copyright:

Eternally Arcane® designs, products, trademarks, photography, descriptions and texts are the exclusive intellectual property of Eternally Arcane® and are protected under the United States copyright laws. They may not be reproduced, duplicated, copied or otherwise exploited for a commercial purpose. The material on this shop or website cannot be edited or modified except by Eternally Arcane®. Any reproduction of original works is a violation of intellectual property law and will be enforced through legal action.

Customer Information:

We receive your information directly from Etsy when you make a purchase and use their services. Your contact details such as your name, address and email are shared with us to process your order.

We may collect the following information:

•  name
•  contact information including email address
•  demographic information such as postcode
•  any information relevant to processing your order such as fulfilling your order and 
   communicating about your order.

We will not sell, distribute or lease your personal information to third parties. We may use your personal information to communicate with you about your order.

✨PROCESSING/SHIPPING TIMES:
Once your order is about to be shipped, you will receive your tracking information via email and in your Etsy account under Purchases. Most orders are generally processed and shipped within 3 to 10 business days, depending on order volume. Please note that during periods of high order volume, processing times may occasionally extend beyond the usual timeframe. Larger orders or orders placed during peak holiday periods may occasionally exceed our usual processing times as well. I am one person handmaking all of these products💜. Your patience is greatly appreciated.

CANDLE SAFETY
Our candles undergo extensive quality and safety testing; however, like all candles, they pose a fire hazard when lit. Many designs include decorative elements such as herbs, florals, which are flammable. We also use crystals. Before lighting, you must remove any decorations, florals, or crystals that could interfere with the wick and ensure proper wick trimming. By purchasing from our shop, you accept full responsibility for following all candle safety precautions. Never leave a burning candle unattended or place it near flammable surfaces. Our candles are primarily decorative and curio items, but are considered fire hazards when lit. Eternally Arcane® is not liable for damages resulting from improper use. Always practice candle safety.

DO YOU USE ESSENTIAL OILS FOR ANY OF YOUR PRODUCTS?
Yes. Most of our products are made with essential oils, including our glass bottled bath salts, milk baths, many of our incenses, ritual oils, and perfume oils. We use quality essential oils to create unique, custom blended scents that are unparalleled. Each scent is carefully curated to vibrationally align with the product, and blended by me personally, creating unique and beautiful scented products. Occasionally, we use essential oil blends, which combine fragrance and essential oils. Please refer to the materials section of each product listing to see whether we use fragrance or essential oils.

I MIGHT BE ALLERGIC TO FRAGRANCE OILS, ESSENTIAL OILS, OR HERBS. DO YOUR PRODUCTS CAUSE ALLERGIC REACTIONS?
The AAD (American Academy of Dermatology) recommends the following steps: Apply the product to a small patch of skin where a person is unlikely to accidentally wash or rub it away. Good areas may include the inside of the arm or bend of the elbow. Apply the product to a quarter-sized patch of skin. A person should apply the product as thickly as they would when using it regularly. Leave the product on the patch of skin for as long as it would normally be on the skin. Repeat the patch test twice a day for between 7–10 days. Wash off and discontinue use if irritation occurs. We are not medical professionals so using any skincare products, or products with herbs, essential oils, or fragrance oils, is at the sole discretion of the customer.

HOW DO I USE YOUR PRODUCT?
There are many books, videos and other information online where you can further your study. Please keep in mind that we are not permitted to provide spiritual advice or mentor. It’s up to the practitioner to know how to use spiritual products and to do their own research.

CANCELLATIONS/EXCHANGES/RETURNS
As stated in our policy, all sales are final. We do not accept cancellations, exchanges, or returns. Our products are handmade, artisan-crafted, and one of a kind. We’re dedicated to providing each customer with a freshly handcrafted item. Additionally, for hygienic reasons, we cannot accept returns. We appreciate your understanding and support in preserving the integrity of our products and brand values. Please review your order carefully before checkout to ensure you have selected the correct items. Thank you!

LEGAL DISCLAIMER
All information provided is for informational purposes only and not a substitute for medical advice. Per Etsy policy, we cannot guarantee outcomes. All spiritual products are sold as curios. Eternally Arcane is not liable for any damages or issues arising from the use or misuse of our products. By purchasing from our shop, you agree to our terms and shop policies. Always consult a medical professional before using herbal supplements or skincare products, especially if you have health concerns. By completing your purchase, you confirm that you have read, understood, agree to our shop policies and safety guidelines, and release Eternally Arcane from any and all liability.
